cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL. 

The paper deals with incremental learning using deep learning approaches and focuses on image recognition tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the use of transfer learning, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and the evaluation is done on ImageNet, which is a popular dataset in the field of natural language processing, hence cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also a possible category.
